dct_title_s: Map of railway systems of Nyasaland and adjoining countries
dct_description_sm: Map shows: railways, proposed railways, and suggested alternative railway routes, light railways, two classes of roads, and tracks.Territorial boundaries and some population centers also shown on map. Original map is filed in the Map and Geospatial Information Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
dct_creator_sm: Mining and Industrial Publications of Africa Ltd
dct_publisher_sm: London : Mining & Industrial Publications of Africa, [1926].
